World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131540578,imgsize-92244.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Sneako says he’s getting married, but there’s more to the story behind viral clip]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131540553.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Internet sensation Sneako sparked widespread speculation with a viral clip announcing his marriage. However, the streamer later clarified in the same video that it was a deliberate joke, highlighting how edited clips can mislead audiences. This revelation left many fans confused, as the initial announcement was shared without full context.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/sneako-says-hes-getting-married-but-theres-more-to-the-story-behind-viral-clip/articleshow/131540553.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/sneako-says-hes-getting-married-but-theres-more-to-the-story-behind-viral-clip/articleshow/131540553.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T01:53:42+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131540552,imgsize-503219.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[KSI’s departure from Sidemen triggers fresh debate after group releases clarifying statement]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131540260.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The Sidemen have released a statement following KSI’s departure from the group. While they said they respect his decision, they revealed that the announcement came before a mutual plan had been agreed upon. The group hoped to organize a proper farewell but said events unfolded differently. Despite the change, the remaining members confirmed they will continue creating content together.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ksis-departure-from-sidemen-triggers-fresh-debate-after-group-releases-clarifying-statement/articleshow/131540260.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ksis-departure-from-sidemen-triggers-fresh-debate-after-group-releases-clarifying-statement/articleshow/131540260.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T00:59:54+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131540254,imgsize-53616.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Twitch star Nmplol breaks silence on divorce settlement with ex-wife Malena Tudi]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131540386.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Twitch streamer Nmplol has disclosed details of his divorce settlement with ex-wife Malena Tudi. The court finalized their marriage under a no-fault insupportability ruling, with most assets split 50/50, though Malena received a larger share of Starforge Systems. Nmplol also revealed incurring over $400,000 in legal fees and expressed relief that the lengthy process is finally over.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/twitch-star-nmplol-breaks-silence-on-divorce-settlement-with-ex-wife-malena-tudi/articleshow/131540386.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/twitch-star-nmplol-breaks-silence-on-divorce-settlement-with-ex-wife-malena-tudi/articleshow/131540386.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T01:16:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131540380,imgsize-732853.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Nick Polom reaches divorce agreement with Malena Tudi following $400,000 legal battle but one settlement detail grabs attention]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131540178.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Nick Polom, better known as Nmplol, has finalized his no-fault divorce from fellow streamer Malena Tudi. According to Dexerto, most assets were divided equally, while Starforge Systems received separate treatment. The court also denied Tudi’s request for monthly spousal support. The outcome has sparked online debate about alimony, asset division, and the financial cost of public breakups.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/nick-polom-reaches-divorce-agreement-with-malena-tudi-following-400000-legal-battle-but-one-settlement-detail-grabs-attention/articleshow/131540178.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/nick-polom-reaches-divorce-agreement-with-malena-tudi-following-400000-legal-battle-but-one-settlement-detail-grabs-attention/articleshow/131540178.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T01:00:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131540159,imgsize-28244.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Canadian man settles in India with wife's family: Cost of living way lower than Toronto, lost 14lbs in 5 months]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131540276.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadian-man-settles-in-india-with-wifes-family-cost-of-living-way-lower-than-toronto-lost-14lbs-in-5-months/articleshow/131540276.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https